<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Good Friday Prayer</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Apr 03, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Tiny gold crosses <br></br>
hang from sparkling <br></br>
gold chains, <br></br>
signs of <br></br>
wealth, affluence, <br></br>
and good taste, <br></br>
compared to <br></br>
a large wooden cross <br></br>
covered in blood, <br></br>
an instrument of torture, <br></br>
a symbol designed <br></br>
to bring terror <br></br>
to enemies of the state.
</p>

 <p>
On this day, Lord, <br></br>
give me a vision <br></br>
of the horror of the cross, <br></br>
for without it <br></br>
there is no beauty <br></br>
of the cross.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


